entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Osto Grissom, a local starship captain, was assaulted by some Meatlumps. It would appear that Meatlumps hate all technology and seek to destroy all of it they can. Osto transports large quantities of electronics for Corellian corporations and therefore became a target.
entries.journal_entry_description: A local starship captain was assaulted on his way out of the cantina. Find out who attacked him and why.
entries.journal_entry_title: CorSec Case Files: Assault and Battery
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with Osto Grissom, the starship captain who was attacked, and find out what happened.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Osto Grissom identified his attackers as Meatlumps. Attack some Meatlumps in the camps near Tyrena to find out who led the attack and why.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The Meatlumps you defeated did not know anything about the assault on Osto Grissom, but they did reveal the location of one of their lieutenants, Ubbal Fenn, in a cave nearby. Go lay waste to the cave to convince Ubbal Fenn to talk to you.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Assault and Battery at the Meatlump Cave
entries.task02_task_display_string_2: Destroy Food Stores in the Cave
entries.task02_task_display_string_3: Destroy Weapon Caches in the Cave
entries.task02_task_display_string_4: Destroy Armor Lockers in the Cave
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Speak with the Meatlump lieutenant, Ubbal Fenn.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Report to Major Walden and brief her on your findings.
entries.task05_item_name: You destroyed a Meatlump armor locker
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Find and destroy some of the Meatlump's armor lockers throughout the cave.
entries.task06_item_name: You destroyed a Meatlump weapon cache
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Find and destroy some of the Meatlump's weapon caches throughout the cave.
entries.task07_item_name: You destroyed a Meatlump food store
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Find and destroy some of the Meatlump's food stores throughout the cave.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Defeat Meatlumps in the cave near Tyrena.
